metadata.name: FAHQ® Metaverse Drip Box #1
metadata.description:
FAHQ® Metaverse Drip Box #1 will be able to claim a collection of metaverse wearables. Each box will receive the same items in terms of type and quantity. However, there will be several variations and rarities of each item. Follow @FAHQ on Twitter for news and updates.

FAHQ® is a lifestyle apparel & skate brand utilizing NFTs for access to limited-edition drops, collections, and collaborations. Learn more: https://www.fahq.com
